<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038975" n="278r"/>
<opener><lb/>Nobilissimo et Celeberrimo Viro
                        <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-11887733X" type="person"><abbr>Joh.</abbr> Poleno</rs><choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> <abbr>S<supplied>.</supplied> P<supplied>.</supplied> D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person"><abbr>NB.</abbr></rs></opener>
  <p><lb/>Nihil mihi accidere potuit gratius quam <rs type="letter" key="B_991170517018005501">liter<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs>, quas mihi
    <lb/>modo attulit Vir doctissimus mihique amicissimus <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1141836866">Lesley</rs>, qui<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>busque mihi occasionem subminitrasti Tibi demonstrandi
                        <lb/>quanto honoris cultu Te Vir Celeberrime prosequar. Ut igitur
                        <lb/>Tibi constet promtus meus in jussa Tua animus significo me
    <lb/>apud <rs type="person">Viduam Koenig</rs><note type="comment">Zur Wittwe König siehe den Kommentar im <rs type="letter" key="B_991170517018005501">Brief von 1715-07-31</rs></note> inquisivisse num adhuc prostarent ii quos
    <lb/>petis <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_88AUNP8T">Ephe<add>m</add>eridum Eruditorum</rs> Libri. Inveni prostar<add>e</add> ibi
    <lb/>omnia Volumina istarum <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_88AUNP8T">Ephemeridum</rs> ab A.<hi rend="sup">o</hi> 1665 usque
                        <lb/>ad annum 1710<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> inclusive. Sunt autem editionis <rs key="place_GEO-2759794" type="place">Amstelodamensis</rs>
<lb/>nec nisi conjunctim vendentur pretio 10<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> Ducatorum <rs key="GeoNamesID" type="place">Hungarorum</rs><!-- ToDo: Währung -->
<lb/>quod si Tibi placeat Volumina h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c pro dicto pretio accipere, meque
                        <lb/>de hoc certiorem facere, promte id quod jusseris exequar. C<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>te<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum pro propensa Tua in me et studia mea
                        <lb/>benevolentia et favore<note type="editorial">Wortumstellung.</note> su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>as ago gratias, Teque ut Tibi persuadeas oro
    <lb/>me amicitiam Tuam qua me dignaris omni officiorum et ob<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/><choice><sic>seqii</sic><corr>sequii</corr></choice> genere <add>omni data occasione</add> demeriturum. Patruus meus <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Joannes</rs> te
    <lb/>quam officiosissime resalutat. </p><closer><salute>Vale et mihi fave.</salute>
<lb/><rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <date when="1715-07-31">pridie Calendarum Sextilium MDCCXV</date>.</closer>
</div>
